               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_23" n="N024"/>(The meaning of the portrait. Expression
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_24" n="N025"/>of the unique individuality)
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_25" n="N026"/>7)<rs type="person" key="Sargent, tillich_person_id__3909"> <hi style="text-decoration: underline;">J. SARGENT</hi></rs> {Mrs. Dyer (Chicago)}
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_26" n="N027"/>Portrait of Henry James
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_27" n="N028"/>(The approximation to the photographic truth)
