               <lb facs="#facs_2_l_14" n="N016"/>of a street.
               <lb facs="#facs_2_l_15" n="N017"/>(The productions of the <hi style="text-decoration: underline;">unconscious</hi>
               <lb facs="#facs_2_l_16" n="N018"/>(surrealistic combination of disrupted pieces of rea-
