               <lb facs="#facs_6_l_25" n="N022"/>     "     Head of Christ.
               <lb facs="#facs_6_l_26" n="N023"/>[Is it as genuine as his harle-
               <lb facs="#facs_6_l_27" n="N024"/>quins?]
